":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"2點仲塞到咁<br />\n運輸署個apps又咩都無講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FefL0MS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFefL0MS.png&h=053eb941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab818dc92c8bf0e72b2ca8c340afc58818bb9390","tid":1205323,"uid":172342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩打算出去<br />\n有個巴打話佢係出面番黎<br />\n見到警察放火"},{"pid":"2d324a9b2672534224a82e939f2e2545dd691112","tid":1205323,"uid":152339,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:16:48.000Z","msg":"凌晨2點咁樣好唔正常，佢地想截查車輛？<br />\n定純粹阻下街？<br />\n定係有事發生"},{"pid":"48989d6aad216fcfa2a014daea2d190b624fb5fe","tid":1205323,"uid":152339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab818dc92c8bf0e72b2ca8c340afc58818bb9390","tid":1205323,"uid":172342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩打算出去<br />\n有個巴打話佢係出面番黎<br />\n見到警察放火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下放咩火？"},{"pid":"3f55e3248c189297536293b7372c35972b64bb63","tid":1205323,"uid":118039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98fe2c4696247c6b734e0f29b87ece8217a60130","tid":1205323,"uid":54876,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"係咪返大陸特訓過？<br />\n所有手法都好有支那風格"},{"pid":"82516ad3bb42521e28e1288f4531d29d8b6fc1b1","tid":1205323,"uid":25342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"啱啱收工諗住換衫出去支援<br />\n見到勁大煙同好多警車，仲有救護車同消防車<br />\n仲有勁大陣燶味"},{"pid":"4c25aa14dad45e91ce4b382b42272005c95fb5fb","tid":1205323,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82516ad3bb42521e28e1288f4531d29d8b6fc1b1","tid":1205323,"uid":25342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:30:48.